darks.codec.wrap
类 ZipWrapper

java.lang.Object
  darks.codec.wrap.Wrapper
      darks.codec.wrap.ZipWrapper

public class ZipWrapper
extends Wrapper

ZipWrapper can ZIP bytes after encoding and UNZIP before decoding. It Support JDK GZIP, JZLIB, COMMON-COMPRESS to ZIP data.

Example: 

  ObjectCoder coder = new ObjectCoder();
      ...
  coder.getCodecConfig().addWrap(ZipWrapper.JZLIB());
      ...
Or 
  ObjectCoder coder = new ObjectCoder();
      ...
  coder.getCodecConfig().addWrap(ZipWrapper.COMMON_COMPRESS());
      ...
Or 
  ObjectCoder coder = new ObjectCoder();
      ...
  coder.getCodecConfig().addWrap(new ZipWrapper(new CustomZipWrapper()));
      ...
